### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

# Note: Run auth.http login first to authenticate session cookie.

# ==============================================================================
# ─── LIFECYCLE STAGES (RBAC rules apply) ──────────────────────────────────────
# ==============================================================================

### List all lifecycle stages (All authenticated users)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lifecycle/stages
Content-Type: application/json

### Update lifecycle stages configuration (Requires Admin or Manager)
POST {{baseUrl}}/lifecycle/stages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stages": [
